{"tid":1414362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工已經撤底失敗","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:33:18.000Z","uid":267783,"like":30,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"64edeee59d78dc3ee208965f64be5eda172043ee","tid":1414362,"uid":267783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"因為每一次個劇本就係做啲嘢，和理非掩護，前線就去撚警燒警<br />\n<br />\n咩五大訴求，咩時代革命，街坊食催淚彈，就係為咗搭個台俾你地攪警察？仲話攪埋宿舍？俾你燒死一個細路老人，係咪好英雄啦？<br />\n<br />\n革你條毛。點解仲要罷工呀，如果做咩事都係搭個台俾你去燒去打？跟住送頭，然後又來過<br />\n<br />\n梁天崎講嘢冇人聽。係囉，前線大撚哂，唔駛反省唔駛改錯。無哂六七月嘅be water，剩係衝同送頭。"},{"pid":"16b882396c01cfe340f0cdd8324172b5fe349e44","tid":1414362,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"咁有咩高見"},{"pid":"b7f434fda86862a4c7c10641f117aa4dd4ee31f3","tid":1414362,"uid":228972,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"16b882396c01cfe340f0cdd8324172b5fe349e44","tid":1414362,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"咁有咩高見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"係咪無高見就代表應該繼續現有策略？"},{"pid":"eb492a01e189b873d82f1276a70d413f8eac695b","tid":1414362,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7f434fda86862a4c7c10641f117aa4dd4ee31f3","tid":1414362,"uid":228972,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"16b882396c01cfe340f0cdd8324172b5fe349e44","tid":1414362,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"咁有咩高見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"係咪無高見就代表應該繼續現有策略？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"一齊返屋企囉"},{"pid":"b26e06115d524dd7be14b38104302dad46cbcead","tid":1414362,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"樓下好多舖有開<br />\n罷乜撚"},{"pid":"171915067807acd4a753962638390fd1f63a4d3b","tid":1414362,"uid":228972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb492a01e